name: Inferno Maw Chiller
text: In the shadowed kitchen of Castle Gormenghast, the Inferno Maw Chiller hummed, its fiery aura waltzing with the dark. It hypnotized the scullery boy with a siren song of heat and hunger. Maidens left ice-picked tributes, lest the Chiller's smoldering appetite awaken, unleashing a banquet of arcane frost.
